{"id":12804,"date":"2023-02-21T12:46:32","date_gmt":"2023-02-21T12:46:32","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/?p=12804"},"modified":"2023-02-21T12:55:28","modified_gmt":"2023-02-21T12:55:28","slug":"healthier-and-happier-deworming-days-for-karen-children","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/healthier-and-happier-deworming-days-for-karen-children\/","title":{"rendered":"Healthier and Happier! Deworming Days for Karen Children"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>According to the WHO, parasitic worms a global issue impacting the health and well-being of millions. They can be particularly detrimental to the growth and development of children and <a href=\"https:\/\/news.harvard.edu\/gazette\/story\/2020\/08\/treating-children-for-worms-yields-health-and-financial-gains\/\">many experts recommend deworming<\/a> in areas where worms are endemic. For many children across Mae Hong Son, the water and environment make parasitic worm infections more likely and this can not only cause dangerous health issues but can also effect concentration, school attendance and overall happiness and mobility. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>After careful consultation with schools, KHT implemented a deworming programme across 7 remote schools and provided deworming medication to over 500 children and also their teachers. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>From evidence, it is shown that deworming days are a more successful way of combatting worms than individuals going to health centres as, worms aren&#8217;t obvious when you first get them. By treating whole schools we combat the issue head on.<\/p><cite>Liv, KHT Programmes Officer<\/cite><\/blockquote>\n\n\n\n<p>This project has been very generously supported by the <strong>Rotary Club of Bangkok South<\/strong>, who have been a long term and invaluable partner to KHT. We hope to complete the second round of the deworming in 6 months and the project has already been very well received by schools and parents! <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1104\" height=\"900\" data-id=\"12806\"  src=\"https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/WhatsApp-Image-2023-01-31-at-10.22.18-e1676982192482.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-12806\" srcset=\"https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/WhatsApp-Image-2023-01-31-at-10.22.18-e1676982192482.jpeg 1104w, https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/WhatsApp-Image-2023-01-31-at-10.22.18-e1676982192482-300x245.jpeg 300w, https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/WhatsApp-Image-2023-01-31-at-10.22.18-e1676982192482-1024x835.jpeg 1024w, https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/WhatsApp-Image-2023-01-31-at-10.22.18-e1676982192482-768x626.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1104px) 100vw, 1104px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" data-id=\"12805\"  src=\"https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/WhatsApp-Image-2023-01-31-at-10.21.57.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-12805\" srcset=\"https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/WhatsApp-Image-2023-01-31-at-10.21.57.jpeg 1200w, https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/WhatsApp-Image-2023-01-31-at-10.21.57-300x225.jpeg 300w, https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/WhatsApp-Image-2023-01-31-at-10.21.57-1024x768.jpeg 1024w, https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/WhatsApp-Image-2023-01-31-at-10.21.57-768x576.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The medication will help remove and prevent parasites and help improve school attendance and participation. KHT&#8217;s team were present for the administering of the medications&#8230;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>We are all thankful and supportive of the deworming days. We are overall very happy with how they went and look forward to many deworming days in the future! Thank you KHT!<\/p><cite>School Headteacher <\/cite><\/blockquote>\n\n\n\n<p>Karen children face many struggles in life as marginalised minorities living in a harsh environment and coping with poverty. KHT works to ensure they can access education and that they are not held back from learning and playing due to something as easily treatable as worms. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can help us continue our important work for Karen children by <a href=\"https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/get-involved\/donate\/\">donating<\/a> today! <\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>According to the WHO, parasitic worms a global&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":4,"featured_media":12807,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_mi_skip_tracking":false},"categories":[55],"tags":[48,50,49,54,52,51,41,53],"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v19.12 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Healthier and Happier! Deworming Days for Karen Children - Karen Hilltribes Trust<\/title>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/karenhilltribes.org.uk\/healthier-and-happier-deworming-days-for-karen-children\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_US\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Healthier and Happier! Deworming Days for Karen Children - Karen Hilltribes Trust\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"According to the WHO, parasitic worms a global...\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https:\/\/karenhilltrib